1.1.0
-----

* Add flags for 3D/WPF notifications: API\Notification\is3DNotification(), API\Notification\isWPFNotification()
* Add API\Notification\renderResponse() method
* Add support for immediate validation when parsing API\Notification
* Add support for alias-based environment setting in GenesisConfig
* Add system requirements verification
* Add LICENSE file
* Fix API\Response initialization
* Fix Network\Wrapper\cURL silent return
* Fix Network\Wrapper\StreamContext error handling
* Fix Genesis Certificate Bundle chain
* Fix illegal XML characters in the request body
* Fix PascalCase support
* Fix Conform to PSR standard
* Change API\Response\getResponseObject() from SimpleXMLElement to ArrayObject
* Remove unused variables in various classes
* Remove namespace shortcuts (use keyword)
* Remove the need for set environment variable, in order to get the CA bundle
* Update PHPSpec and its dependencies
* Update PHPDoc comments
* Update file headers

1.0.2
-----

* Add support for internationalization (currently only in WPF)
* Add flag (API\Response\isPartiallyApproved()) for partially-approved transactions
* Add helper method API\Response\getFormattedAmount()
* Add helper method API\Response\getFormattedTimestamp()
* Add Network\Wrapper\StreamContext configuration based on the PHP version
* Fix transaction amount conversion between ISO-4217 and Nominal
* Update PHPDoc comments
* Update Specs

1.0.1
-----

* Move the ISO-4217 currency handling to the post-processing
* Fix API\Response\isSuccessful() returning wrong status on some transaction types
* Fix Utils\Currency types
* Update PHPDoc Comments
* Update README
* Update Specs

1.0.0
-----

* Initial version